   Technology:
   Two Computing Leaders Have New Plans
   ---
   Microsoft Intends to Boost
   Windows and Undercut
   IBM-Supported OS/2
   ----
   By G. Pascal Zachary
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
07/29/91
</DATE>
